    <item>
      <title>Reddit 正在通过 Subreddit 征求用户对其财报电话会议的提问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/reddit-will-answer-user-questions-in-may-7-earnings-call</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Reddit Inc. 周四表示，该公司将于 5 月 7 日发布自公开募股以来的第一份收益报告。 Reddit 还将在 Reddit 子版块中向用户征求问题 – r/RDDT——除了分析师的常规询问外，还会在财报电话会议上回答这些问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/reddit-will-answer-user-questions-in-may-7-earnings-call</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 20:39:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国曾有机会引领芯片制造技术，但却错过了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/quicktake/euv-chipmaking-how-us-lost-control-of-cutting-edge-semiconductor-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是一次史无前例的战略失误。美国在开发支撑当今人工智能革命的半导体技术方面发挥了至关重要的早期作用。然而，现在是一家荷兰公司垄断了这一工艺，而亚洲制造商则主导了生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/quicktake/euv-chipmaking-how-us-lost-control-of-cutting-edge-semiconductor-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 20:30:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国警告各机构可能因微软黑客攻击而遭受破坏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/us-issues-emergency-directive-amid-fears-agencies-were-breached</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心俄罗斯民族国家黑客组织可能访问了一些信件，美国联邦机构被命令分析电子邮件、重置受损凭证并努力保护微软公司云帐户的安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/us-issues-emergency-directive-amid-fears-agencies-were-breached</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 20:26:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能炒作刺激 IPO 后，Reddit 和 Astera 面临分析师评论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/reddit-astera-face-analyst-reviews-after-ai-hype-spurs-hot-ipos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Reddit Inc. 和 Astera Labs Inc. 赢得了投资者的青睐，纷纷涌入人工智能领域。到了周一，上个月帮助其上市的银行分析师将尝试权衡其涨势是否合理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/reddit-astera-face-analyst-reviews-after-ai-hype-spurs-hot-ipos</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 19:22:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管环球音乐存在争议，泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的歌曲仍重返 TikTok</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/taylor-swift-songs-back-on-tiktok-amid-universal-music-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管泰勒·斯威夫特的唱片公司和社交视频平台之间存在持续争议，但她的音乐仍重新出现在字节跳动有限公司的 TikTok 上。恰逢她的最新专辑《The Tortured Poets Department》即将于 4 月 19 日发行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/taylor-swift-songs-back-on-tiktok-amid-universal-music-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 18:29:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
